snippet.textDisplay: Honestly,bullies just want attention.Once in like,3rd grade I believe,I told someone who I thought I could trust that I was upset that Everytime we did a play,the principals daughter would get the female lead.I wrote a note to the girl I thought I could trust,I'll call her A.And she took it and showed it to everyone in the class.(we were a 3rd-5th grade class,A was a 5th grader)I heard this and started crying so the teacher pulled me into the hallway.She told me I shouldn't spread rumors,even though I didn't.A got in 0 trouble.We then watched a video about including People and being nice and things like that.Didnt work because a few weeks later the principals daughter had a sleepover and I was the only girl not invited.I heard they bullied A at the sleepover and pretended to go to sleep to get rid of her.I talked to A and her and I are still friends.She left the school a month or so after.Then my bff left.Then basically all of my "friends"(they were backstabbers)left and then the school year ended.My grandpa died during the summer.I later made new friends and one of them used to be a bully of mine.So yeah idk just my story.

snippet.textDisplay:
._. I been bullied before and went through this process
My bully thought it would be funny to put tooth paste in my hair brush (I had a bad case of tangled hair & like to keep my hair tangled free). Ofc I know it was her but I ask the teacher (who though I did it to myself idk why) to go to the restroom to try to clean it out. When I came back somehow she stole my friend's phone and put it in my backpack without anyone knowing. So my friend is fricking out I was trying to help her find it! The bully said "Maybe your friend stole it (me cuz I was her only friend in that class). So the teacher asked me to give her my backpack to search , I let her do so. Lord behold my friend's phone! I told her that I did not steal the phone that it must had been [insert bully's name]. (she had a big smirk on her face)


So the teacher just send both of us to the Principal's office. The Principal looked at me "The phone was found in the in your backpack. . . I'm sorry but I an going to have to suspend you for 5 days".
I was like wtf. My bully looking like she is the victim was saying I was the bad person and doing fake tears to make her story more believable. Sadly I had an issue with bottling up emotion soo... I kinda snap(?) Telling the Principal all she done to me and told him " I never touched the phone. If you call the police right now I guaranteed that her fingerprints would be there and not mine. I am willing to take a lie detector (at the time I thought it was 100% true) it will tell you I am telling the truth about the phone and . . ." He cuts me off "10 days of detention young lady! If you come in MY office again with that additue I will make you repeat your grade. DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME?! " Even tho I wanted to say more it was probly best for me to not say anything else.


So I wasn't super pissed about the toothpaste in my hair or the other stuff she did before that. What really got me was her stealing and pending it on me I wanted her to pay for her action. Sadly that never happen and instead I became super anti-social after this and lost a friend on that same day. I know I should of never "blown up" on the Principal and that only made it worst. But I do hope my bully became a better person today then how she was in the past.

I said no because it had been a gift from my great grandfather.  He in retern grae my hand and bit down on my finger so hard that it broke the skin in some places.  I did't go to the hospital because we lived in the middle of nowhere.  So as a punishment my school made us sew and embroder an I'm sorry pillow if we did somthing wrong and my stupid kindergarden teacher made me sew a pillow and comforted the little brat because he had lied and sayed that it was his truck.  To explain the bitting he said somthing to the extent of "she was hitting me!" and so I got to spend the rest of the day sitting in a corner hand embrodiring a pillow which I later slaked the kid over the head with, he was a jerk and my teacheres told my parents the kids lie and to this day they still think that I lie about everything.
